<br>
Focusing on one aspect of a class and comparing that aspect to another class is rarely useful, however.  BLs can increase the level of their pet.  Give their pet a proc.  Heal it for more than we can heal ours...and a ton of other things that make them BL. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/useravtrev.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SeravTrev</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#333333>(6/20/02 4:52:09 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=468.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   No question</span><hr size=1> All beastlords have going for their pets are some nice heals.<br>
